full_text: Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 755 Filed 08/10/22 Page 33 of 262 1738 LC8VMAX2 Gill Velez - cross 1 Ms. Gill, you indicated that you've worked for the property management company for approximately 15 years; correct? 2 A. Correct. 3 Q. Which means you started in approximately 2007? 4 A. Correct. 5 Q. And the document that was introduced in connection with your testimony concerns the date of 2000; correct? 6 A. Correct. 7 Q. You have no personal knowledge of how this document was completed; correct? 8 A. No. 9 Q. You have no personal knowledge of any of the information on this document; correct? 10 A. The information I know is what was written in it. 11 Q. Right. But you had nothing to do with putting it on this? 12 A. No. 13 Q. And you had nothing to do with how records were kept prior to you joining the management property company in 2007; correct? 14 A. Correct. 15 MS. STERNHEIM: No further questions. Thank you. 16 THE COURT: Thank you, Ms. Sternheim. 17 Mr. Rohrbach. 18 MR. ROHRBACH: No redirect, your Honor. 19 SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300 DOJ-OGR-00013311
